
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to stackoverflow</title>
</head>
<style>
    body{
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }
    h1{
        color: #000;
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 500;
        text-align: center;
    }
    p{
        color: #000;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
        text-align: center;
    }
    a{
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #000;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 400;
        text-align: center;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
    }
    a:hover{
        background-color: #000;
        color: #fff;
    }
</style>
<body>
    

    <h1>Welcome to stackoverflow</h1>
    <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for signing up for stackoverflow.</p>
    <p>Click on the link below to verify your email address.</p>
    <a href="{{url}}">Verify Email</a>
    <p>Thanks,</p>
    <p>Stackoverflow Team</p>
</body>
</html>